  <h1>Lab Setup &amp; Environment</h1>

        <div class="diagram-container">
          <img src="/images/fundamentals/lab-topology.svg" alt="Lab topology: Kali attacker, Windows 10 domain client, Windows Server DC, Metasploitable, and C2 server all connected on host-only 192.168.56.0/24 network">
